  Goan2 u7 tiaN7-tioh8 e5 ku7-koan3, khi3 tham3 ka-ki7 e5 kou3-hiong. Goa2 e5 pun2-chhu3 u7 ho2 e5 ke2-chi2 theh8, ia7 u7 chin choe7 chhin-ai3 e5 peng5-iu2, chhin-chhiuN7 goan2 chit poe3-e5. Chit8 e7-pou goa2 kap pe7-bu2, hiaN-ti7, chi2-be7 beh khi3 tham3 goan2 e5 pun2-hiong; chong2-si7 hit cha-khi2 loh8 toa7 hou7. Che hou7 goan2 chin sit-bang7. In-ui7 goan2 tioh8 che7 be2-chhia saN li2 lou7 e5 hng7, sou2-i2 na7 loh8 hou7 chiu7 boe7 tit khi3. Goa2 siuN7 tioh8 sit-loh8 chit khoan2 e5 ki-hoe7, soa3 chhin-chhiuN7 boe7 thun-lun2-tit e5 khoan2. 
  Hit-si5 goa2 iok-liok8 si7 chap8-chhit he3;goa2 khah-cha2 bat oat8-liam7 Si-phian 31 phiN, tui3 hit phiN goa2 khi2-thau5 tit-tioh8 Hok-im e5 Oe5. Goa2 e5 sim-lai7 teh hoan5-lo2 loh8 hou7 e5 su7, hit si5 soa3 siuN7-tioh8 chit chat kong2, ¡§Goa2 e5 ho7-hok si7 li2 sou2 tiaN7-tioh8-e5.¡¨ Au7-lai5 goa2 chiu7 siuN7, ¡§Loh8-hou7 e5 si5-ki5 kap hou7 hou7 soah, che long2 si7 I sou2 tiaN7-tioh8-e5, I tak8 hang7 beh siat-hoat ho2-se3.¡¨ ¡§Long2 si7 ti7 I e5 chhiu2-thau5,¡¨ che si7 chit8 kha oe5, koh chit8 kha chiu7-si7 ¡§I long2 beh siat-hoat ho2-se3.¡¨ 
  Goa2 tit-tioh8 thau5 chit8 siang Hok-im chin-sit8 e5 Oe5, goa2 chiu7 ka7 i chheng7-teh. Loh8-hou7 si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 tiaN7-tioh8-e5, I tek-khak bo5 chho3-gou7; tui3 oa2-kho3 I, hit cha2-khi2 e5 iu-bun7 kap poe7-gek8, soa3 piN3-chhoe3 hoaN-hi2 kap ho5-peng5. I hou7 jit8 chhut hian2-beng5 I e5 ka3-si7, sou2-i2 goan2 long2 oe7 tit khi3. 
  Koh kui2-na7 geh8-jit8, chit siang oe5 pang-chan7 goa2 keng-ke3 chit8 tiau5 chin khun3-lan5 e5 lou7. Goa2 u7 tiaN7-tioh8 e5 sim-chi3 ai3 jip8 Ko-teng2 Hak8-hau7, ia7 u7 siat chit8 e5 hong-hoat thang chheng-kiat chit tiau5 lou7, hou7 i bo5 chou2-tong3. Chong2-si7 kau3 be2 goa2 e5 lau7-pe7 m7 chun2 (goa2 chit si5 chai i e5 taN2-sng3 chin ho2, chong2-si7 hit si5 iau2 m7 chai ), sou2-i2 goa2 soa3 sit-bang7 chhin-chhiuN7 e2-kau2. 
  M7-ku2 goa2 bo5 sit-loh8 goa2 e5 oe5. ¡§Che long2 si7 ti7 I e5 chhiu2-thau5,¡¨ chit kha oe5 tu2-tu2 chiau3 goan5, oan5-choan5 koh sui2. ¡§I teh siat-hoat tak8 hang7 ho2-se3,¡¨ chit kha ia7 si7 chiau3 goan5, iong2 koh kian5-kou3. Hit e7-pou goa2 iau2-ku2 lau5 bak8-sai2 tiap-a2-ku2, chong2-si7 si7 un-ho5 kap teng5-sin e5 bak8-sai2, sou2-i2 goa2 e5 sim hoaN-hi2 gim5-si chhin-chhiuN7 chiau2-a2. ¡§An2-ni chin ho2-se3, in-ui7 Siong7-te3 teh siat-hoat tak8 hang7, I ia7 chin thiaN3 goa2.¡¨ 
  Goa2 thau5-chit8 siang e5 oe5 si7 ¡§ho5-peng5 hok-im e5 pi7-pan7,¡¨ chhin-chhiuN7 Si-phian 31 phiN 15 chat sou2 ki3-chai3. Chong2-si7 ti7 Ma2-thai3 10: 29-31, tui3 chit saN chat, li2 oe7 tit-tioh8 toa7 song2-khoai3. ChhiaN2 hian Seng3-keng khoaN3, soa3 choe3 ki3-ho7. Li2 bo5 ku2 tek-khak ai3 khiam3-eng7 in. 
  ThiaN3-thang3 siau3-lian5 e5 peng, siat-su2 li2 tu2-tioh8 tai7-chi3, hou7 li2 siu7-siong, sit-taN2 kap kan-lan5, tioh8 ki3-tit che si7 in-ui7 li2 thng3-chhiah-kha lai5 kau-chian3. Tioh8 chheng7 chit siang oe5, tioh8 chin soe3-ji7 m7-thang pang3-sak. Au7-lai5 chit ku3 oe7 chiu7 oe7 chiaN5 choe3 chin-sit8, ¡§Li2 e5 oe5 beh chhin-chhiuN7 tang5 thih, ia7 li2 e5 khui3-lat8 kau3 li2 chit8-si3-lang5 chiah soah.¡¨ Chit chat si7 Sin-beng7-ki3, li2 oe7 chhe7 chhut lai5 choe3 ki3-ho7 a2-boe7 ? 
  Goa2 ai3 kong2-khi2 u7 lang5 sit-loh8 in e5 oe5 e5 su7. hou7 lin2 thang tui3 in tit-tioh8 ka3-si7. Nga2-kok khoaN3-kiN3 Iok-sek bak huih e5 saN, ¡§i boe7 siu7 an-ui3, ia7 kong2, Goa2 tek-khak pi-ai kau3 ti7 bong7-nih8, chiu7-kun7 goa2 e5 kiaN2 chiah soah.¡¨ I eng-kai tioh8 to3 hoan2 kong2, ¡§Chiah-e5 long2 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 chi2-i3 I oe7 siat-hoat ho2-se3.¡¨ Siong7-te3 ko2-jian5 long2 siat-hoat ho2-se3, Nga2-kok eng-kai tit-tioh8 an-ui3. Chong2-si7 i u7 sit-loh8 i e5 oe5. 
  Nga2-kok thiaN-kiN3 kong2 Ai-kip8 e5 toa7-koaN ai3 khoaN3 Pian7-nga2-bin2, i e5 sim chhin-chhiuN7 beh piak-phoa3. I kong2,¡§Iok-sek kap Se-bian7 i2-keng bo5 ti7-teh, koh beh chhoa7 Pian7-nga2-bin2 khi3, chiah-e5 long2 si7 siong-hai7 goa2.¡¨ Siat-su2 i na7 u7 chheng7 i e5 oe5, i eng-kai kong2, ¡§Chiah-e5 bo5 m7 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 chi2-i3, I long2 beh chhoa7 in to3-tng2 kau3 ho2-se3.¡¨ Siong7-te3 ko2-jian5 chhoa7 in chhut, ia7 Nga2-kok eng-kai tioh8 siu7 an-ui3. Chong2-si7 i u7 sit-loh8 i e5 oe5. 
  Hoat-lo2 ku7-choat8 m7 kiong-kip I2-sek-liat8 peh-siN3 sio-chng e5 chhau2, hit si5 in e5 chok8-tiuN2 siu7 piN-phah, in-ui7 peh-siN3 sou2 choe3 e5 kang-tiaN5 boe7 chiau3-ku7 chhin-chhiuN7 u7 kiong-kip chhau2 hit e5 giah8-siau3. Mou5-se in-ui7 kha bo5 chheng7 oe5, sou2-i2 ti7 kau-chian3 e5 tai7-seng hiam2-hiam2 sit-loh8 khui3-lat8, Chhut Ai-kip8-ki3 5:22, 23. I siuN7 tak8 hang7 su7 long2 bo5 kong-hau7. Siat-su2 i na7 u7 chheng7 i e5 oe5 i tioh8 kong2, ¡§Hoat-lo2 kap thong Ai-kip8 kok long2 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 chhiu2, I beh long2 chhoa7 I e5 peh-siN3 chhut.¡¨ Siong7-te3 ko2-jian5 an2-ni choe3; siat-su2 Mou5-se na7 bo5 sit-loh8 i e5 oe5, i sou2 keng-ke3--e5 chiu7 long2 u7 thang siu7 an-ui3. 
  Lou7-be2 goa2 ai3 po3 lin2 chai goa2 kui2-na7 ni5 cheng5 sou2 tit-tioh8 e5 oe5. ¡§Hoan7-su7 tioh8 kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3, in-ui7 ban7 hang7 su7 bo5 m7 si7 li7-ek thiaN3 Siong7-te3 e5 lang5.¡¨ ChhiaN2 lin2 chhi3-khoaN3; che si7 chin sui2,chin ki5-koai3 e5 oe5. Sit8-chai7 oe7 hou7 chhi3-a2 piN3-choe3 hoe, hou7 iu-bun7 choe3 hoaN-hi2. Te7 it ho2 chiu7-si7 lin2 thang tit-tioh8 chhin-chhiuN7 sui5-pian7 e5 le2-mih8. 
  IV. Sin3 e5 Tin5-pai5
  Lan2 i2-keng kang2-kiu3 chin-sit8 e5 toa3, gi7 e5 hou7-sim-kiaN3 kap ki5-iN7 e5 oe5; chiah-e5 oe7 pang-chan7 li2 keng-ke3 khun3-lan5 e5 lou7, m7-na7 un2-tang3, koh u7 chin e5 an-ui3. TaN lan2 tioh8 gian2-kiu3 Sin3 e5 Tin5-pai5. 
  Seng3-chheh ka7 lan2 kong2, lan2 u7 oah8 e5 tui3-tek8, i put-si5 kou3-siu2 teh sia7 ¡§he2-chiN3¡¨ beh siong-hai7 lan2, in-ui7 an2-ni lan2 chiah khiam3-eng7 tin5-pai5. Siat-su2 lan2 na7 bo5 tin5-pai5 thang phah-biat8 chiah-e5 chiN3, tui3-tek8 chiu7 khah-iaN5, lan2 chiu7 su. 
  Lan2 e5 Chu2 ti7 khong3-ia2 siu7-chhi3 e5 si5, tui3-tek8 eng7 he2-chiN3 sia7 I, ia7 I chaiN2-iuN7 ti2-tng: chit hang7 chiu7-si7 choe3 eng7 tin5-pai5 te7-it ho2 e5 bou5-hoan7 hou7 lan2 thang oh8. 
  Tui3-tek8 tit-tioh8 ho2 ki-hoe7 thang chhi3 Chu2 Ia5-sou, in-ui7 I si3-chap8 mi5-jit8 bo5 chiah8 put-chi2 iau. Mou5-kui2 ka7 I kong2,¡§Li2 na7 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 KiaN2, chiu7 kah. chiah-e5 chioh8 piN3 choe3 piaN2,¡¨ Chong2-si7 Ia5-sou Ki-tok i2-keng u7 chit8 ku3 Seng3-keng pian7-pian7 ti7 sim-lai7, I ti7 tui3-tek8 e5 bin7-cheng5 sui5-si5 in2-khi2 kong2, ¡§U7 ki3-chai3 kong2, Lang5 e5 oah8, m7-na7 oa2-kho3 piaN2, chiu7-si7 oa2-kho3 Siong7-te3 e5 chhui3 sou2 chhut long2-chong2 e5 oe7.¡¨ ChhiaN2 chu3-i3, chhin-ai3 siau3-lian5 e5 peng. siat-su2 I na7 bo5 ki3-tit hit ku3, I beh chaiN2-iuN7 oe7 eng7 i choe3 tin5-pai5 ? 
  Au7-lai5 mou5-kui2 chhoa7 I kau3 kek8 koaiN5 e5 sou2-chai7, chiu7-si7 tian7 e5 be2-liu, ka7 I kong2, ¡§Li2 na7 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 KiaN2, tioh8 ka-ki7 tio5-loh8-khi3; in-ui7 u7 ki3-chai3 kong2, I beh beng7-leng7 I e5 thiN-sai3, eng7 chhiu2 hu5 li2, bian2-tit li2 e5 kha tak-tioh8 chioh8.¡¨ Chong2-si7 Chu2 Ia5-sou iu5-goan5 u7 pat8 chat e5 Seng3-keng pian7-pian7 thang in3, ¡§Koh u7 ki3-chai3 kong2, Boh8-tit chhi3 Chu2 li2 e5 Siong7-te3.¡¨ Chit e5 i3-su3 chiu7-si7 kong2, Siong7-te3 na7 u7 kong2 sim2-mih8, lan2 thang sin3-kho3 I, in-ui7 I i2-keng kong2-chhut, lan2 m7-bian2 ka7 I chhi3 si7 chin a2-si7 ke2. Ki5-tian5 tu2-tu2 ti7 chia choe3 sit-chho3. Siat-su2 i na7 u7 Sin3 e5 Tin5-pai5 pian7, tui3-tek8 chiu7 boe7 chhe7 ki-hoe7, hou7 i eng7 iuN5-mng5 lai5 chhi3 Siong7-te3. Kiam2-chhai2 hit si5 Ki5-tian5 Seng3-chheh bo5 kau3-giah8 sek8. 
  Mou5-kui2 koh-chai3 chin ho2-taN2 lai5 kong-kek. I ti7 tiap-a2-ku2 e5 tiong-kan eng7 thiN-e7 ban7 kok kap eng5-hian2 hou7 Ia5-sou khoaN3, ka7 I kong2, ¡§Li2 na7 phak-loh8 pai3 goa2, chiah-e5 goa2 long2 beh hou7 li2.¡¨ Ki-tok siu7 chit khoan2 e5 chhi3 sit8-chai7 si7 kau3-kek8 lah. Iau2-ku2 lan2 e5 Chu2 bo5 siu7-khi3; I koh eng7 I e5 tin5-pai5 lai5 ti5-hong5 kong2 ¡§Sat-tan3, the3-khi3; in-ui7 u7 ki3-chai3, Eng-kai pai3 Chu2 li2 e5 Siong7-te3; tok8-tok8 hok8-sai7 I na7-tiaN7.¡¨ 
  ¡§Au7-lai5 mou5-kui2 li7-khui I, u7 thiN-sai3 kau3, lai5 su7-hau7 I.¡¨ Tak8 pai2 e5 ki-chhi3, I long2 tek-seng3; in-ui7 Seng3-chheh sou2 ki3-e5, I put-chi2 sek8; sou2-i2 tak8 pai2 e5 chhi3. I oe7 theh8-chhut tu2-ho2 e5 chiuN chat, thang phah-biat8 i. 
  Tai7-pit8 gim5-si kong2, ¡§Goa2 eng7 Li2 e5 oe7 khng3 ti7 sim-lai7 (chiu7-si7 oat8-liam7 ki3 ti7 sim-lai7 ), goa2 chiah bian2 hoan7-choe7 ti7 Li2¡¨ I chin un-khun5 teh choe3 Sin3 e5 Tin5-pai5. M7 chai lin2 u7 an2-ni mah? Siat-su2 li2 u7 pat8 hang7 e5 kho3-theng5 chin bo5 eng5, ia7 bo5 chit e5 tin5-pai5, chiu7 ti7 chhi3-lian7 e5 jit8, li2 beh chaiN2-iuN7 choe3 ? 
  Chhin-ai3 siau3-lian5 e5 peng, li2 ti7 kau-chian3 e5 si5, na7 ai3 khia7-chai7, chiu7 ti7 siau3-lian5 e5 si5 tioh8 ki3-tit thang siu-khng3 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7. Goa2 ai3 ka7 lin2 kong2 tam7-poh8. Chiu7-si7 chit e5 tin5-pai5, kun7-lai5 sou2 keng-ke3 e5 thoan3-lian7. Chit8 am3 thiN-chhiN kng-kng, chit8 e5 soe3-han3 gin2-na2 cheng-sin5, boe7 koh khun3 khi3. Hit si5 toa7 e5 tui3-tek8, eng7 chan5-jim2 e5 he2-chiN3, sia7 chit e5 cheng-sin5 e5 gin2-na2 kong2, ¡§Thau chau2-khi3 goa7-bin7 ban2 hit liap8 sui2 e5 pheng5-ko2.¡¨ Hit si3-ui5 e5 sou2-chai7, chi2 u7 hit liap8 pheng5-ko2 na7-tiaN7. Si7 ku7-ni5 chhun-thiN cheng3 ti7 sin e5 ke2-chi2-hng5, khi2-thau5 sou2 siN-e5; sou2-i2 choan5-ke e5 lang5 eng7 chit-e5 choe3 chin-chiaN3 u7 chhu3-bi7 e5 mih8. 
  Hit e5 gin2-na2 un5-a2 peh-khi2-lai5, chiu7 tui3 lau5-thui loh8-khi3; ke-lai7 e5 lang5 long2 teh khun3. Am3-si5 e5 keng2-ti3 chin ho2, koh sok-cheng7; sui-bong2 thiN-chhiN sio2-khoa2 kng, iau2-ku2 hit tiau5 lou7 i put-chi2 sek8. Hit si5 chit8 liap8 toa7 e5 thiN-chhiN teh khoaN3 i, i sim-lai7 soa3 bo5 peng5-an. I hut-jian5 ki3-tit Ha7-kah e5 oe7 kong2, ¡§Siong7-te3 teh kam3-chhat goa2.¡¨ Che si7 cheng5 le2-pai3 i e5 lau7-bu2 sou2 ka3 i--e5. I tiu5-tu5 liam7 kui2-na7 pian3 kong2, ¡§Siong7-te3 teh kam3-chhat goa2.¡¨ I kiaN-hiaN5 koh sio2-khoa2 khoaN3 hit liap8 thiN-chhiN, chiu7 oat8-to3-tng2 tiam7-tiam7 peh-chiuN7 lau5-teng2, ia7 eng7 than2-a2 kah bat8 i e5 bin7. Tui3 i e5 sin3, i chai hit ku3-oe7 si7 chin-sit8; sou2-i2 chiaN5-choe3 Sin3 e5 Tin5-pai5, thang phah-biat8 i gui5-hiam2 e5 chhi3-lian7, hou7 i bo5 khi3 thau-ban2 hit liap8 pheng5-ko2. Seng3-chheh ki3-chai3 kong2, ¡§Siong7-te3 teh kam3-chhat goa2.¡¨ Chit ku3 chiu7 chin kau3-giah8 lah. 
  Chit8 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 khun3-chhiN2 khi2-lai5, beh choe3 kang, hit jit8 e5 kang-tiaN5 put-chi2 choe7. Hit si5 tui3-tek8 ti7 i e5 sin-piN, ia7 chai chit e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 hou7 put-chi2 choe7 tai7-chi3 pe2-pak8 i. 
  Sou2-i2 i chiu7 ka7 hu7-jin5-lang5 kong2, ¡§Li2 m7-thang thak8 Seng3-keng, in-ui7 li2 bo5 kau3-giah8 e5 si5-kan, thang choe3 li2 kin-a2-jit8 sou2 eng-kai tioh8 choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 pun2-hun7.¡¨ Che sit8-chai7 si7 chin tok8 e5 chiN3 I chai chit ki chiN3 na7 it-seng tiau5 ti7 chit e5 hu7-jin5-lang5, i chiu7 bo5 ai3 thak8 Seng3-keng, au7-lai5 chiu7 bo5 khui3-lat8 thang ti2-tng i. 
  Chong2-si7 I2-li7-a kap song3-hiong e5 chiu2-koaN2 hu7-jin5-lang5 e5 kou3-su7, i tui3 cha2-cheng5 chiu7 i2-keng ki3 ti7 sim-lai7. I chit si5 khiam3-eng7, sui5-si5 theh8-chhut, pian7-pian7 thang ti2-tng tui3-tek8. I2-li7-a ka7 chiu2-koaN2-hu7 tho2 chit8 e5 soe3 e5 piaN2 e5 si5, i kong2 boe7 tit thang hou7 i, in-ui7 chhun tam7-poh8 thang choe3 ka-ki7 e5 lou7-eng7 na7-tiaN7. Chong2-si7 sian-ti in3 i kong2,¡§Tai7-seng choe3 chit8 e5 soe3 e5 piaN2 hou7 goa2: in-ui7 Ia5-ho5-hoa u7 kong2, choe3 piaN2 e5 mi7-hun2 boe7 kiam2, kau3 Goa2 loh8-hou7 e5 si5 chiah soah.¡¨ Chiah-e5 i3-su3 i chin beng5-pek8. U7 siaN ka7 i kong2, ¡§Tai7-seng thak8 poaN3 tiam2 cheng ku2 e5 Seng3-keng: in-ui7 Ia5-ho5-hoa u7 kong2, sou2 chhun e5 si5-kan, u7 kau3-giah8 thang choe3 li2 sou2 khiam3-eng7-e5.¡¨ 
  Tui3 chit e5 khoah-toa7 e5 eng3-un2, hit e5 chhi3-lian7 e5 he2-chiN3 sui5-si5 phah-biat8. Tui3 hit si5 i tak8 cha2-khi2 chhut-lat8 thak8 Seng3-keng, ia7 hou7 i tit-tioh8 po2-poe3, chiu7-si7 sou2 be7 bat u7-e5. Sou2 eng3-un2-e5 eng3-giam7. Ki5-u5 e5 si5-kan chhiong-chiok, m7-na7 choe3 i sou2 ai3 choe3-e5, koh oe7 choe3 i e5 Chu2-lang5 sou2 ai3 i choe3 e5 su7; an2-ni long2 kau3-giah8 bo5 khiam3-kheh. 
  Chin choe7 tioh8-siong, phoa3-siuN3 e5 sin3-chia2, che si7 sim2-mih8 ian5-kou3? Kiam2 m7 si7 in-ui7 in eng7 chin-sit8 e5 oe7 khng3 ti7 chheh-siuN, bo5 khng3 ti7 sim-lai7 mah? Tui3-tek8 teh eng7 chiN3 sia7 li2 e5 si5, li2 tek-khak bo5 si5-kan thang chau2-khi3 li2 e5 chheh-siuN chhe7 Seng3-chheh. 
